item.title: Again 001
item.description: So I’m here again, rebuilding in a massive backlog of failures, one again and again there is still people cheering up on me I was thinking could be a normalized depression field or this is normal in me I feel like I made so much progress only to see nothing out nothing new same view and now I must go out because my time here is up? is been always up, no more of me here I guess.

item.title: Tryhard-Reborn Protocool
item.description: I hear Jerusalem bells A-ringin' Roman cavaldry choris are singing! The first thing I did this morning was sing, lungs out, I feel so much discomfort I must die, this must end, no more. Les's see if the Grit has and end. I must face my fears and burn my dread in order to ascend I must burn the stigma no and for all - It’s unfair It’s weird but if that so.

item.title: Subito - Capito
item.description: El tiempo pasa, muy Rapido y muchas veces no nos damos cuenta no solo de él si no del impacto de otras vidas en la nuestra. Estoy agradecido, de retribuir la confianza que pusieron en mi. Gracias totales que el mar de Ether no diluya tu impresionante presencia. Connection established. Transmission complete. Present day, present time. Another entry logged into the wired…

item.title: Good morning Vietnam
item.description: I wake up early this morning, is cold, I’m barefoot- underwear, and my long coat, I hate eating in the morning makes me feel all bloated , also drugs hit better with a empty stomach I hear my many alarms sound over and over, but I’m awake - I’m here, i can turn the off one by one but after hearing them , I must know the time I’m wasting or spending.

item.title: Computers and more machines
item.description: You’re part of the moon of the light of every atom I interact with and I’m so i’m love I can’t scream I can’t speak I never been so tight of hands of mind of love . . . Oh dear I wasn’t ready for any of this but I’m still here HEre I’m like a ship that never left that nobody wants so in the air left to rot

item.title: Corrupt Data 062
item.description: I got so used to run that I’m still on it #I’m soo fill with pain, with hate, with love, they don’t stop so getting more intense. shorty shorty shorty shorty, get the fuck out of my mind is not a place for you. I mean why lit me up? why burn the pyre why the rot expands ticking seconds, less telomers for me and you, tell me inmortal machine, how it feels a empty eternity with not promised afterlife?

item.title: Corrupt Data 001
item.description: Se supone que me deberia sentir mejor no asi. no asi. ¿porque? ¿es culpa mia? So i can say she want solo, you can say, cuz she can get way I wanna get rid of all, all these feelings, all these memories I wanna be painless, soulless as you say you are. Do you feel, pain do you? I feel every tissue screaming for something real and this is not this is just a DEAD END FABRICATED DEAD END NO WHERE TO RUN IMPROVE

item.title: La Dama de Hierro no Puede dormir!
item.description: Siempre atenta siempre vigilante, La dama de hierro no puede dormir, ella mira siempre al horizonte, buscando, 1000 batallas fueron ya, ¿900? no se puede saber, su cuerpo cubierto de hierro esta. El hechizo que la hizo tan fuerte, no la deja descansar, el oxido, mella, corroe, duele. Aquí estoy, cierra los ojos un segundo yo miro por ti, deja la lanza descansar, Dama de hierro en batalla ya no estas, flores en ti crecen, Dama de hierro siempre fuerte, descansa, Dama de hierro en batalla ya no estas, mira la hoguera no forja espadas, el rey no comanda, las flechas no se venden y tu debes descansar.
